comments[4]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-03-08T22:07:09.126Z",maintainer-agent,"pm list and pm list-all are currently identical. Fix: pm list should exclude terminal statuses by default."
  "2026-03-08T22:12:48.671Z",maintainer-agent,"Implementation complete. Changed: list.ts (excludeTerminal option in ListOptions + applyFilters), main.ts (normalizeListOptions returns ListOptions, registerListCommand adds excludeTerminal param, pm list wired with excludeTerminal=true). Updated: PRD.md, README.md (new pm list vs pm list-all section), CHANGELOG.md. Tests: added excludes-terminal-statuses test case in list-command.spec.ts. Result: 536/536 tests pass, 100% coverage maintained."
  "2026-04-03T11:55:43.941Z",codex-agent,"Mapped external-audit Issue 9: resolve list status-filter UX confusion via command surface and/or explicit help guidance updates."
  "2026-04-03T11:59:29.272Z",codex-agent,"Wave3 scope: list status-filter UX fix must preserve current list/list-all semantics for existing scripts unless explicitly opting into new flags."
